      "role": "user",
      "content": "i think im losing it or something but i saw something weird today. i was looking at this old brass clock in a shop window and i saw this weird flicker, like a flash of red light inside the gears. like ten minutes later, a car drove by and crashed right there and there was red paint everywhere. it felt like i saw it happen before it actually did. has this ever happened to you? like seeing things before they happen?",
